originalText.text:
E Terra has been so supportive and instrumental in allowing our nonprofit to expand our operations while we searched for a full time space. With their beautiful kitchen, amazing equipment and the kindest staff, we've been able to cook and serve 600/meals a week to the homeless and those in need.

E terra staff have come to volunteer with us, they have a beautiful community service program and really care. They always were willing to work with us and make sure we had the cooking and storage space we needed, and were helpful and accomodating.

I love working in the kitchen, meeting other cool chefs and businesses and enjoying the space. It's got large, bright windows, friendly and open, and clean and organized. My life as a baker changed with the big mixers! Thank you e. Terra for all you provide to the community.

originalText.text: Recently attended a really fun Industry Pizza Night event at e.terra Kitchen.  They had a full house, with amazing pizza, great speakers and a great vibe!  Looking forward to attending their next event!

originalText.text: I’m currently a member at Eterra and have had an excellent experience.  Their kitchens are huge, clean, well equipped, with every appliance and item you need provided.  They have ample dry and cold storage and a supportive team who is there to help small food businesses succeed.  It’s the best shared kitchen I have worked in as a caterer in NYC.

originalText.text:
I hosted a cooking class at e.terra and everything went splendidly.

After booking my date and coordinating my prep time, everything else fell into place.

The kitchen is spacious, most appliances available for use (always good to ask), clean and spacious.

Since it is a shared kitchen, you are alotted a counter for prep and fridge/freezer space if needed.

Many thanks to the staff and managememt of e.terra kitchen.

originalText.text: I have had multiple photoshoots at e.terra Kitchen. There’s great natural light and plenty of space for lighting equipment & other gear. Great for chefs & bakers if they need a professional kitchen environment. My go to place for culinary assignments!
